# Стандартизация данных для нормальной отрисовки Q-Q plot
scaler = StandardScaler()
df['RUB_scaled'] = scaler.fit_transform(df['RUB'].values.reshape(-1, 1))
df['KZT_scaled'] = scaler.fit_transform(df['KZT'].values.reshape(-1, 1))


def plots(x):
  fig = plt.figure(figsize=(30,10))
  ax_1 = fig.add_subplot(1, 3, 1)
  ax_2 = fig.add_subplot(1, 3, 2)
  ax_3 = fig.add_subplot(1, 3, 3)
  
  # distribution plot
  fig1 = sns.distplot(x, fit=stats.norm, kde=False,bins=50, ax=ax_1)
  # Q-Q
  pplot = sm.ProbPlot(x)
  fig2 = pplot.qqplot(line="r", ax=ax_2)

  # P-P
  pplot = sm.ProbPlot(x)
  fig3 = pplot.ppplot(line="r", ax=ax_3)
  plt.show()

plots(df["RUB_scaled"])
plots(df["KZT_scaled"])

def central_stat(x):
  plt.figure(figsize=(10,5))

  sns.distplot(x, fit=stats.norm, kde=False, bins=50)

  plt.axvline(st.mean(x), 0, 1, label='Среднее', color='red')
  plt.axvline(st.median(x), 0, 1, label='Медиана', color='blue')
  if (x is df["RUB"]):
    x = np.round(x)
  plt.axvline(st.mode(x), 0, 1, label='Мода', color='black')

  plt.legend(fontsize=16)
  plt.show()


central_stat(df['RUB'])
central_stat(df['KZT'])

def print_info(x):
  if (x is (df["RUB"])):
    print("--------- RUB ---------")
  elif (x is df["KZT"]):
    print("--------- KZT ---------")
  print("Среднее: ", st.mean(x))
  print("Медиана: ", st.median(x))
  if (x is df["RUB"]):
    x = np.round(x)
  print("Мода: ", st.mode(x))
  print("\n")

print_info(df['RUB'])
print_info(df['KZT'])

def create_norm(x):
  loc, scale = stats.norm.fit(x)
  n = stats.norm(loc=loc, scale=scale)
  return n

print("Тест Калмогорова-Смирнова для RUB:", stats.kstest(df["RUB"], create_norm(df["RUB"]).cdf))
print("Тест Калмогорова-Смирнова для KZT:", stats.kstest(df["KZT"], create_norm(df["KZT"]).cdf), "\n")

print("Тест Андерсона-Дарлинга для RUB:", stats.anderson(df["RUB"], 'norm'))
print("Тест Андерсона-Дарлинга для KZT:", stats.anderson(df["KZT"], 'norm'), "\n")

print("Тест Шапиро-Уилка для RUB:", stats.shapiro(df["RUB"]))
print("Тест Шапиро-Уилка для KZT:", stats.shapiro(df["KZT"]), "\n")

print("-------Грязные данные-------")
print(df[["RUB","KZT"]].describe())

def crop(df, column, left=0.05, right=0.95):
    left = df[column].quantile(left)
    right = df[column].quantile(right)
    return df[(df[column] > left) & (df[column] < right)].copy(deep=True)


df = crop(df[["RUB","KZT"]], "RUB")
df = crop(df[["RUB","KZT"]], "KZT")

print("\n-------Чистые данные-------")
print(df.describe())

def show_criteria(label, method, x, y):
  criteria_val, criteria_p = method(df[x],df[y])
  print(label, " R =", criteria_val, "    | p= ", criteria_p)

show_criteria("Kendall correlation: ", stats.kendalltau, "RUB", "KZT")
show_criteria("Pearson correlation: ", stats.pearsonr, "RUB", "KZT")
show_criteria("Spearman correlation: ", stats.spearmanr, "RUB", "KZT")

def show_regression(x, y, axis):
  axis.scatter(df[x],df[y])
  m, b = np. polyfit(df[x], df[y], 1)
  axis.plot(df[x], m*df[x]+b)

fig, ax = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(20,10))

show_regression("RUB", "KZT", ax[0])
show_regression("KZT", "RUB", ax[1])
